{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I wanted to emphasize was that while Fry were sent there to rescue these enemies of, you know, the people really on the list, and mostly artists, and writers, and musicians, and politicians, and all, anybody who was in danger could always be helped by him.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He would help them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if he couldn't help them, he would give them money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had-- they found a gangster who would take the money, give money here, and then his clients would take it in America or in Switzerland or wherever, and we had ways of doing that.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That wasn't difficult.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Roosevelt, I think, helped in that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the money came in from Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roosevelt and her group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as it went on and on and was getting more and more successful, then it was much easier to-- although, sometimes we ran awfully low.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going-- and then my money was coming from this friend of mine, Bill Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had quite a bit, and he was waiting for me to go to the RAF with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was hanging out and just-- he didn't help us very much because he looked too German, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He looked-- but it was good to be seen with him because he looked German, and he was German descent.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had driven an ambulance with me during the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he went with me to the RAF, and he was shot down on his third flight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And another one who was in the ambulance corps waited for us in Lisbon, and then on the ship going over, he was sunk and killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I guess not a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not quite a year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know the dates and all.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
